name: YO(U)˟
description:
˟Why am I here? and where is my life, I have no energy to stand and where are you?
Where is the heat of the eternal summer? the heat of lovers and bandits.
Im tired and I dont want to be here, the sun is shining without heat and the light are not white enought.
Where am I? why without you?
˟˟˟˟˟
